<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA97">
<l>piṭicēr kaḷiṟaḷitta pērāḷā vuṉṟa</l>
<l>ṉaṭicērn taruḷpeṟṟā ḷaṉṟē – poṭicē</l>
<l>raṉaṟkaṅkai yēṟṟā ṉavircaṭaimēṟ pāynta</l>
<l>puṉaṟkaṅkai yeṉṉumpeyarp poṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O great man who took care of the bull elephant joined with [its] female,</l>
<l>joining your feet she obtained grace, did she not, [that] gold  with the name</l>
<l>called Gaṅgā , the stream that flows down on the shining matted hair of him</l>
<l>who received the fire in [his] palm, joined with ashes?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
